<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.6">
<l>cemperun taṭaṅkaṇ ṇaṉtiraḷ tōḷaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">tēvaki ciṟuvaṉ tēvarkaḷ ciṅkam</l>
<l>nampara maṉin nāḷkuḻa lūtak</l>
<l rend="indent">kēṭṭavar kaḷiṭa ruṟṟaṉa kēḷī</l>
<l>ramparam tiriyuṅ kāntappa rellā</l>
<l rend="indent">mamutakī tavalai yālcuruk kuṇṭu</l>
<l>nampara maṉṟeṉṟu nāṇima yaṅki</l>
<l rend="indent">naintucōrn tukaimmaṟit tuniṉṟa ṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Listen to the distressing experiences</l>
<l>of those who heard when our Supreme lord</l>
<l rend="indent">–He with the big, broad, red eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">He with the bulging arms</l>
<l rend="indent">Devakī’s boy, Lion of the Gods–</l>
<l>played [his] flute today!</l>
<l>All the Gāndharvas who wander the heavens were caught</l>
<l>by the net of [his] nectar[-like] song,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying, “Our burden is no more”,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming shy and bewildered,</l>
<l rend="indent">languishing and dispirited,</l>
<l>they stood, restraining their hands.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
